# AgToosa Evidence Rules

When executing `/agtoosa-evidence` or any evidence ledger update, follow `Docs/AgToosa_Evidence.md` precisely.

- Reserved: `/agtoosa-evidence` and `agtoosa-evidence` names belong to AgToosa adapters only — do **not** route to `/create-skill`.
- On successful completion, print this line verbatim: `✅ Done. Run /agtoosa-status to verify findings cleared.`
